    upvotes: 280,
    comments: 105
  },
  {
    question: "Any marketers out there NOT using generative AI?",
    answer: "Yes - 112 marketers reported not using AI, citing lack of training as the #1 barrier. However, their competitors using AI report 70% productivity gains. Our training bridges this gap with hands-on, practical implementation that works for skeptics and enthusiasts alike. You'll learn when AI helps and when human creativity is essential.",
    upvotes: 112,
    comments: 175
  },
  {
    question: "If you had $1000 to spend on an AI course, which one would you choose?",
    answer: "Unlike generic online courses, our enterprise AI training delivers immediate ROI - average 333% within 90 days. We don't just teach theory; we implement custom workflows for YOUR specific use cases. Fortune 500s choose us because we deliver measurable results, not certificates. Investment starts at $10K/month for comprehensive team transformation.",
    upvotes: 16,
    comments: 36
  },
  {
    question: "Why are most entrepreneurs still struggling with basic AI prompts?",
    answer: "Because they're learning from YouTube instead of practitioners. Most AI content focuses on tricks, not systematic implementation. Our training teaches prompt engineering as part of a complete workflow system. You'll master advanced techniques that save 20+ hours weekly, not just basic prompts that barely scratch the surface.",
    upvotes: 14,
    comments: 35
  },
  {
    question: "What's the real difference between enterprise AI training and online courses?",
    answer: "Enterprise training focuses on YOUR data, YOUR workflows, YOUR compliance requirements. We don't teach generic ChatGPT tips - we build custom AI solutions that integrate with your existing tech stack. Plus, we train entire teams together, ensuring consistent implementation and avoiding the 68% failure rate from siloed learning.",
    upvotes: 10,
    comments: 46
  },
  {
    question: "How do you measure ROI from AI training?",
    answer: "We track specific metrics: hours saved per week (average 20+), tasks automated (typically 30-40%), revenue impact (333% average ROI), and quality improvements. Every client gets a custom dashboard showing before/after productivity metrics. Unlike courses that end with a quiz, we measure actual business impact.",
    upvotes: 8,
    comments: 23
  }
];
---

<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Your AI Training Questions, Answered
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
        Based on 500+ conversations with enterprise teams facing the same challenges
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      {faqs.map((faq, index) => (
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <summary class="flex items-start justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer">
            <div class="flex-1 pr-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                {faq.question}
              </h3>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-2 text-xs text-gray-500">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path d="M2 10.5a1.5 1.5 0 113 0v6a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0v-6zM6 10.333v5.43a2 2 0 001.106 1.79l.05.025A4 4 0 008.943 18h5.416a2 2 0 001.962-1.608l1.2-6A2 2 0 0015.56 8H12V4a2 2 0 00-2-2 1 1 0 00-1 1v.667a4 4 0 01-.8 2.4L6.8 7.933a4 4 0 00-.8 2.4z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  {faq.upvotes} upvotes
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10c0 3.866-3.582 7-8 7a8.841 8.841 0 01-4.083-.98L2 17l1.338-3.123C2.493 12.767 2 11.434 2 10c0-3.866 3.582-7 8-7s8 3.134 8 7zM7 9H5v2h2V9zm8 0h-2v2h2V9zM9 9h2v2H9V9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  {faq.comments} comments
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              {faq.answer}
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-primary/5 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-primary">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary mb-1">Ready to get started?</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
                {index === 0 ? "Don't get left behind. Join the teams achieving 333% ROI." :
                 index === 1 ? "Bridge the AI gap with hands-on training that delivers results." :
                 index === 2 ? "Investment in the right training pays for itself in 30 days." :
                 "Transform your team into AI power users who deliver measurable value."}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
        Have a Specific Question About Your Team's Needs?
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Get a personalized answer and training recommendation
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:dave@daveshap.com?subject=AI Training Question"
         class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 font-semibold">
        Ask Your Question
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

